ww.v2ex.com/u/123128xyz", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/cbe9fb364138757f76e872e0ca8ee5f1?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/cbe9fb364138757f76e872e0ca8ee5f1?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/cbe9fb364138757f76e872e0ca8ee5f1?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1643703509, "last_modified": 1782739315, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "RyougiShiki", "last_touched": 1783117208, "title": "我预判，第一波 AI 洪峰已过！", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1224778", "created": 1783065265, "deleted": 0, "content": "AI coding 趋势终于拐点了！\r\n\r\n**我预判，第一波 AI 洪峰已过。**\r\n\r\n\r\n据我观察**4 个方面**:\r\n\r\n1 、第三方价格数据(暴跌，需求减少)：\r\n\r\nGeminiPro 一年会员自动开通 CDK 包绑卡订阅 **¥12**\r\n\r\nChatGPT  [带 RT ]  [ Plus 成品号]  **¥15**\r\n\r\n2 、v 站数据（话题占比下降）：\r\n\r\n据观察 V 站上月 AI 话题占比趋近 100%，当前占比也有下降趋势\r\n\r\n3 、个人数据：\r\n\r\n短期使用量，也明显下跌。不可能永远有新项目，只有初版稳定之后就不会再有暴力 token 需求。\r\n\r\n4 、小红书数据：\r\n\r\n前段时间->vibe coding 帖子热度极高。\r\n\r\n很多**不懂代码的人**。\r\n\r\n偶然有一个/多个想法->开通 ai 会员(短期)->生成 app （养猫\\遛狗\\逗娃..）\r\n\r\n后面在于推广维护，短期很难再有一个新想法。\r\n\r\n**看懂趋势比埋头苦干更有价值！**\r\n\r\n真的需要，**说说大家的感觉**，比如公司使用，个人观察，中转站数据？", "content_rendered": "<p>AI coding 趋势终于拐点了！</p>\n<p><strong>我预判，第一波 AI 洪峰已过。</strong></p>\n<p>据我观察<strong>4 个方面</strong>:</p>\n<p>1 、第三方价格数据(暴跌，需求减少)：</p>\n<p>GeminiPro 一年会员自动开通 CDK 包绑卡订阅 <strong>¥12</strong></p>\n<p>ChatGPT  [带 RT ]  [ Plus 成品号]  <strong>¥15</strong></p>\n<p>2 、v 站数据（话题占比下降）：</p>\n<p>据观察 V 站上月 AI 话题占比趋近 100%，当前占比也有下降趋势</p>\n<p>3 、个人数据：</p>\n<p>短期使用量，也明显下跌。不可能永远有新项目，只有初版稳定之后就不会再有暴力 token 需求。</p>\n<p>4 、小红书数据：</p>\n<p>前段时间-&gt;vibe coding 帖子热度极高。</p>\n<p>很多<strong>不懂代码的人</strong>。</p>\n<p>偶然有一个/多个想法-&gt;开通 ai 会员(短期)-&gt;生成 app （养猫\\遛狗\\逗娃..）</p>\n<p>后面在于推广维护，短期很难再有一个新想法。</p>\n<p><strong>看懂趋势比埋头苦干更有价值！</strong></p>\n<p>真的需要，<strong>说说大家的感觉</strong>，比如公司使用，个人观察，中转站数据？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1783065487, "replies": 71, "id": 1224778}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1777132346", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1777132346", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 239655, "footer": "", "header": "<!--\r\n一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。\r\n-->", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1777132346", "stars": 4497, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 701340, "username": "sharkCapt", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/sharkCapt", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/fb93/d40e/701340_mini.png?m=1731312712", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/fb93/d40e/701340_normal.png?m=1731312712", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/fb93/d40e/701340_large.png?m=1731312712", "created": 1721211628, "last_modified": 1731312712, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "macha", "last_touched": 1783084897, "title": "为什么称 Gemini 是“美国豆包”？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1224689", "created": 1783046587, "deleted": 0, "content": "经常看到有人说 Gemini 是“美国豆包”，这应该不是一个褒义词吧。\r\n\r\n想请教下大家，这个梗主要是吐槽它的哪个方面，是因为写代码太拉胯吗？\r\n\r\n我经常在 aistudio ( https://aistudio.google.com/) 查一些生活类的问题，比如汽车、医疗、历史相关等。我感觉比 GPT 的网页版或者国内的一些网页端都要好用一些。而且相比 ChatGPT 动不动就上下文超限，Gemini 主要优点是免费额度多。\r\n\r\n所以想和大家探讨两个问题：\r\n1. 为什么 Gemini 会喜提“美国豆包”的称号？大家是在什么场景下觉得它很难用的？\r\n2. 顺便问下，大家平时网页端的主力模型是哪个？", "content_rendered": "<p>经常看到有人说 Gemini 是“美国豆包”，这应该不是一个褒义词吧。</p>\n<p>想请教下大家，这个梗主要是吐槽它的哪个方面，是因为写代码太拉胯吗？</p>\n<p>我经常在 aistudio ( <a href=\"https://aistudio.google.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://aistudio.google.com/</a>) 查一些生活类的问题，比如汽车、医疗、历史相关等。我感觉比 GPT 的网页版或者国内的一些网页端都要好用一些。而且相比 ChatGPT 动不动就上下文超限，Gemini 主要优点是免费额度多。</p>\n<p>所以想和大家探讨两个问题：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>为什么 Gemini 会喜提“美国豆包”的称号？大家是在什么场景下觉得它很难用的？</li>\n<li>顺便问下，大家平时网页端的主力模型是哪个？</li>\n</ol>\n", "last_modified": 1783046587, "replies": 61, "id": 1224689}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1733731195", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1733731195", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 71867, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1733731195", "stars": 9720, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 604260, "username": "Teresa789", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/Teresa789", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1fd1/4bbf/604260_mini.png?m=1779259552", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1fd1/4bbf/604260_normal.png?m=1779259552", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1fd1/4bbf/604260_large.png?m=1779259552", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1fd1/4bbf/604260_xlarge.png?m=1779259552", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1fd1/4bbf/604260_xxlarge.png?m=1779259552", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1fd1/4bbf/604260_xxxlarge.png?m=1779259552", "created": 1669866346, "last_modified": 1779259552, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "BillGates", "last_touched": 1783100203, "title": "现在备案域名的流程又臭又长", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1224707", "created": 1783048562, "deleted": 0, "content": "最近申请了域名备案，发现不仅过管局，还要在公安联网备案。这公安联网备案的网站是真的垃圾，网页端注册一半让你去下个 app ，下完 app 用刚注册的账号登录还登录不进去，然后又重新注册一遍，看了 ios 商店里全是骂这勾八 app ，搞不懂都在工信部备案了为啥还要同样的信息再在公安在搞一遍，你要说多加一道流程捞经费我也认了，我 chovy 啊，你捞油水倒是把网站和 app 做好了啊", "content_rendered": "最近申请了域名备案，发现不仅过管局，还要在公安联网备案。这公安联网备案的网站是真的垃圾，网页端注册一半让你去下个 app ，下完 app 用刚注册的账号登录还登录不进去，然后又重新注册一遍，看了 ios 商店里全是骂这勾八 app ，搞不懂都在工信部备案了为啥还要同样的信息再在公安在搞一遍，你要说多加一道流程捞经费我也认了，我 chovy 啊，你捞油水倒是把网站和 app 做好了啊", "last_modified": 1783048562, "replies": 57, "id": 1224707}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1777132346", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1777132346", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 239655, "footer": "", "header": "<!--\r\n一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。\r\n-->", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1777132346", "stars": 4497, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 475708, "username": "xiaoxiaodong", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/xiaoxiaodong", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d6c7/79ca/475708_mini.png?m=1770610219", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d6c7/79ca/475708_normal.png?m=1770610219", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d6c7/79ca/475708_large.png?m=1770610219", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d6c7/79ca/475708_xlarge.png?m=1770610219", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d6c7/79ca/475708_xxlarge.png?m=1770610219", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d6c7/79ca/475708_xxxlarge.png?m=1770610219", "created": 1583830012, "last_modified": 1770610219, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "cybort", "last_touched": 1783078869, "title": "发现了一个悖论，给大家来个乐子", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1224672", "created": 1783044077, "deleted": 0, "content": "按照常理热空气应该上升，冷空气下降\r\n\r\n目前处于夏天，观察的现象是地表的空气非常热，高空的空气温度非常低，不符合常理。\r\n\r\n------\r\n不用科学解释，逗大家一笑", "content_rendered": "按照常理热空气应该上升，冷空气下降<br /><br />目前处于夏天，观察的现象是地表的空气非常热，高空的空气温度非常低，不符合常理。<br /><br />------<br />不用科学解释，逗大家一笑", "last_modified": 1783044077, "replies": 53, "id": 1224672}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "h